{"tid":831962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國慌了？華爾街日報：中取消訪美團","createTime":"2018-09-22T12:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T00:05:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0cb014641f6f889520b43525ce946c4525697069","tid":831962,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"美國慌了？華爾街日報：中取消訪美團<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%8C%E4%BA%86-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98-070018771.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%258C%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%2598-070018771.html&d=OKT7wwAq0alXNoREpGbchDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=066b76fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%8C%E4%BA%86-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98-070018771.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普本周一宣布將對價值2000億美元的中國商品加徵10%關稅，中國也對600億美元的美國商品加徵5%到10%不等的關稅來回擊，《華爾街日報》更是於今（22）日報導，傳出中國對兩國將要展開的貿易會談「喊卡」。<br />\n<br />\n兩國為緩和緊張局面，原訂下周要展開貿易會談，北京將派出代表團前往華府，此舉也是為了接下來國務院副總理劉鶴訪美鋪路，不過，根據《華爾街日報》的消息來源，這兩個代表團的赴美計畫都已經被中國取消。<br />\n<br />\n美媒《CNBC》指出，針對中國赴美展開貿易會談的計畫，兩國對話已持續了數周，不過這些努力，被川普周一的加徵關稅宣布給破壞殆盡，現在美國財政部長史蒂芬&middot;梅努欽（Steven Mnuchin）正努力重啟與中國的貿易會談。"},{"pid":"878091628ae74f90cdcb68cccf0e428b4bf21ffc","tid":831962,"uid":28353,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"中國大勝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4666f1959d9d025358301db18738135f1ca4063","tid":831962,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" 